title: Leftfield - Leftism [Leftism]
description:
Leftism is the debut album by electronica musicians Leftfield, released in 1995. In a 1998 Q magazine poll, readers voted it the eightieth greatest album of all time, while in 2000 Q magazine placed it at number 34 in its list of the 100 Greatest British Albums Ever.
